<SectionWrapper>
    <SectionLeft>
        <h2>Positions</h2>
        <p>Set the position of the off canvas by setting the attribute of <Code>@(@"<OffCanvas Position=""position-left"">")</Code></p>
        <p>position-left, position-right, position-top, position-bottom</p>

        <h2>Example</h2>
        <p><Code>@(@"<OffCanvas Position=""position-left"" Absolute=""true"">")</Code> will make sure the offcanvas is in the page content.</p>
        <HighlightCS Language="html" Full="true" HeaderIcon="mdi-language-html5" HeaderBGcolor="#5d2b90" HeaderTitle="Razor"
                     Content="" />

        <Button DataToggle="offCanvasLeftSplit1">Open Left</Button>
        <Button DataToggle="offCanvasRightSplit2">Open Right</Button>

        <GridContainer>
            <GridX>
                <Cell Size="small-6">
                    <OffCanvasWrapper>
                        <OffCanvas Id="offCanvasLeftSplit1" Position="position-left" Absolute="true">
                            <p>Off Canvas Content</p>
                        </OffCanvas>
                        <OffCanvasContent style="min-height: 300px;">
                            <p>I have nothing to do with the off-canvas on the right!</p>
                        </OffCanvasContent>
                    </OffCanvasWrapper>
                </Cell>
                <Cell Size="small-6">
                    <OffCanvasWrapper>
                        <OffCanvas Id="offCanvasRightSplit2" Position="position-right" Absolute="true">
                            <p>Off Canvas Content</p>
                        </OffCanvas>
                        <OffCanvasContent style="min-height: 300px;">
                            <p>Im a unique off-canvas container all on my own!</p>
                        </OffCanvasContent>
                    </OffCanvasWrapper>
                </Cell>
            </GridX>
        </GridContainer>

    </SectionLeft>
</SectionWrapper>

<SectionWrapper>
    <SectionLeft>
        <h2>Directions</h2>
        <p>Off-canvas can open from any direction, left, right, top, and bottom.</p>
        <p>Note: if you have some sticky stuff or other floating things, make sure to add z-index in style of the <Code>@(@"<OffCanvas></OffCanvas>")</Code> component is higher than the floating things' index.</p>
        
        <h2>Example</h2>
        <HighlightCS Language="html" Full="true" HeaderIcon="mdi-language-html5" HeaderBGcolor="#5d2b90" HeaderTitle="Razor"
                     Content="" />

        <Button DataToggle="offCanvasLeft1">Open Left</Button>
        <Button DataToggle="offCanvasRight1">Open Right</Button>
        <Button DataToggle="offCanvasTop1">Open Top</Button>
        <Button DataToggle="offCanvasBottom1">Open Bottom</Button>
        <OffCanvasWrapper>
            <OffCanvas Id="offCanvasLeft1" Position="position-left" style="z-index:15;">

            </OffCanvas>
            <OffCanvas Id="offCanvasRight1" Position="position-right" style="z-index:15;">

            </OffCanvas>
            <OffCanvas Id="offCanvasTop1" Position="position-top" style="z-index:15;">

            </OffCanvas>
            <OffCanvas Id="offCanvasBottom1" Position="position-bottom" style="z-index:15;">

            </OffCanvas>
        </OffCanvasWrapper>

    </SectionLeft>
</SectionWrapper>

<SectionWrapper>
    <SectionLeft>
        <h2>Transitions</h2>
        <p>There are really 2 transitions <Code>push</Code> and <Code>overlap</Code>.</p>

        <h2>Example</h2>
        <p><Code>@(@"<OffCanvas Position=""position-left"" Absolute=""true"">")</Code> will make sure the offcanvas is in the page content.</p>
        <HighlightCS Language="html" Full="true" HeaderIcon="mdi-language-html5" HeaderBGcolor="#5d2b90" HeaderTitle="Razor"
                     Content="" />


        <OffCanvasWrapper>
            <OffCanvas Id="offCanvasOverlap" Position="position-left" DataTransition="overlap" Absolute="true">

            </OffCanvas>
            <OffCanvas Id="offCanvasPush" Position="position-left" DataTransition="push" Absolute="true">

            </OffCanvas>
            <OffCanvasContent style="min-height: 250px;">
                <Button DataToggle="offCanvasOverlap">Open Overlap</Button>
                <Button DataToggle="offCanvasPush">Open Push</Button>
            </OffCanvasContent>
        </OffCanvasWrapper>

    </SectionLeft>
</SectionWrapper>

